{"tid":709613,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實波台有好多人都比老豆老母虐待而變態既例子","createTime":"2018-06-20T07:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T16:02:36.000Z","uid":102240,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"141c98dd1f52a0244e7bfc00bcbd516f6445e0a3","tid":709613,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"阿古路老母成日打佢，最激果鑊係拎電蚊拍打臉（上次有出黎飲酒既清可以做證）遺傳身高得160，呢架雖然發左達但都成日打女人<br />\n<br />\n2b細個包皮唔甩，老豆水佢夾硬用力扯甩，最後爆晒血去急症縫針，雖然呢架條野無問題，但我覺得呢件事點都影響到佢變左成日1night stand，就係想話比人知自己條野好粗<br />\n<br />\nN賓兒童之家大(背景唔知)，仲要係裡面比人其他孤兒排斥，呢架大個左d政治思想都怪怪地...廿幾歲人仲撐黃洋達...<br />\n<br />\n希望大家同呢3位手足傾計盡量唔好傷口灑鹽"},{"pid":"328e58de87b888d46242eaeb631c00a1c1f92b5a","tid":709613,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"a0f0f5c16b905154643698495c108d8f219be255","tid":709613,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"老豆水佢夾硬用力扯甩，最後爆晒血去急症縫針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f19980728b228b5cfb3ba26b3bee6c1982188b","tid":709613,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac766c43b20ef31e727ffef2d797ceca82593b5","tid":709613,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿古路佢弱智嫁"},{"pid":"808792fdabbd369a1a777a9d56462ad20ae3ebf5","tid":709613,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:10:49.000Z","msg":"咩咩妹 嫁俾我好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f220382c7afc28f2f4e17ac4aecae58f4eb934c1","tid":709613,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"808792fdabbd369a1a777a9d56462ad20ae3ebf5","tid":709613,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB